      <title>美国警告中国将采取协调行动反对俄罗斯的战争支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/us-warns-china-of-coordinated-action-against-russian-war-support</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两名美国高级官员周五表示，美国将与盟友协调，惩罚帮助俄罗斯加强军工基础的中国企业，包括可能对金融机构实施制裁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/us-warns-china-of-coordinated-action-against-russian-war-support</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 20:41:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
